dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.systemtemplate.fibex.fibexcore.corecommunication

Interface IMultiplexedPart

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDynamicPart, IStaticPart

    public interface IMultiplexedPart
extends IEntity
    IMultiplexedPart: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    According to the value of the selector field the dynamic part can have a different layout. For each alternative there is one COM I-Pdu that is transmitted in the dynamic part. The static part of the multiplexed I-Pdu is the same regardless of the selector field and consists of one Com I-Pdu.
